## xxd-basic
$ echo -n "Hello" | xxd
00000000: 4865 6c6c 6f                             Hello

## xxd-limit
$ echo -n "Hello, World!" | xxd -l 5
00000000: 4865 6c6c 6f                             Hello

## xxd-offset
$ echo -n "Hello, World!" | xxd -s 7
00000007: 576f 726c 6421                           World!
